msgstr "``live_price_acquire_channel``"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "实时价渠道，如 `eastmoney`"
msgstr "Canales de precios en tiempo real, como `eastmoney`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
